Dear Mrs Marash,

Please find the Second Preliminary Offering Memorandum and a redline agains=
t the 1st POM now available in the dataroom. Kindly let me know if you have=
 any issues accessing/viewing it.

Please note below the transaction timeline. We would kindly ask you to fund=
 your purchase amount into the BNYM escrow account by Thursday, 24th Septem=
ber or Friday, September 25th at the very latest. Can you please confirm th=
at you are able to meet the funding timeline?

Transaction Timeline:

  *   Pricing date will be Thursday, 24th September
  *   We would ask you to fund your purchase amount into the BNYM escrow ac=
count by Thursday, 24th September or Friday, September 25th at the very lat=
est
  *   Closing will take place on Monday, 28th September

Please let us know if you have any outstanding questions.

Thank you,
Imogen


